{"type": "article", "id": 9404, "title": "Nendo 曲木家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-11T07:22:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235244vj2rNz6AJkMCFdOs.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t日本设计工作室 Nendo 最近和维也纳家具商 Gebrüder Thonet Vienna 合作推出了一款 “Single-Curve”（“单曲线”）曲木家具，包括凳子，高脚凳，餐桌等。这款作品在保持该品牌曲木特征的同时，加入 Nendo 的设计简约而精致的设计风格，直线与曲线的紧密结合反而让整体更具张力。Nendo 相信很多人已经很熟悉了，这里是 <a href=\"http://www.gebruederthonetvienna.com/index.php\" target=\"_blank\">Gebrüder Thonet Vienna 的官方主页</a>，可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235241Hd1TsroQ8FhxalUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352418bTKip6hgO4sSW3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235241QzKRUZ4eTCOjgYXI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235242bEMIhmLPT6notO7e.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235242Sxp6wAN5ltnroqui.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235242I5GNeCZyABgUkKnh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235243DwKyL2GzUC1raI4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235243ItMdBghA5Ei40pfz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}